KitKat::

With lightening fast reflexes, she turned, jumped the ring roped in 
one leap, and ran towards Maxima. "YOU! You do not raise your voice 
to me young one. I do not care who you think you are. You will show 
the proper respect. I am the trainer here. You are the interloper. If 
you want to play games, then leave and do your programming 
elsewhere." she said, growling. Her optics red with fury, and the fur 
on the back of her neck standing up. "You will learn your place young 
one. In the pack, there is an order. And in that order, I am your 
supior officer."  She took a step back to recompose herself. 

In a more steady and lightly softer tone. "You, young one are clever, 
smart and well knowledged. But you have yet to really learn how to 
use this talent to it's fullest potential. When you have, then you 
shall be leader. Untill then, I am still higher ranked. You will show 
the rank respect if not the bot. Much like Hydras. He has my loyalty 
and respect. And I shall show that to all who are around me. You will 
do well to do the same."

She turned and went back to the ring. Her arm still holding her 
stomach.
